description: Disassociates a set of queues from a routing profile.

parameters.name: InstanceId
parameters.description: The identifier of the Amazon Connect instance. You can find the instance ID in the Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the instance.

parameters.name: RoutingProfileId
parameters.description: The identifier of the routing profile.

parameters.name: QueueReferences
parameters.description: The queues to disassociate from this routing profile. (dict) --- Contains the channel and queue identifier for a routing profile. The identifier for the queue. The channels agents can handle in the Contact Control Panel (CCP) for this routing profile.

nested_params.name: Channel
nested_params.description: The channels agents can handle in the Contact Control Panel (CCP) for this routing profile.
